graph TB
    subgraph "NeMo Guardrails Server"
        direction TB
        API["FastAPI/Uvicorn Server<br/>Port 8000/TCP"]
        Engine["Guardrails Engine<br/>Rails Pipeline"]
        Colang["Colang Runtime<br/>v1.0 / v2.x"]
        Embeddings["Embeddings Engine<br/>SentenceTransformers / FastEmbed / ONNX"]
        KB["Knowledge Base<br/>Annoy Index / RAG"]
        Library["Guardrails Library<br/>Content Safety, SDD, Hallucination,<br/>Jailbreak, Topic Safety, Regex"]
        Tracing["OpenTelemetry Tracing<br/>Span Extractors"]

        API -->|routes requests| Engine
        Engine -->|executes flows| Colang
        Engine -->|semantic similarity| Embeddings
        Engine -->|retrieval augmentation| KB
        Engine -->|applies rails| Library
        API -->|instruments| Tracing
        KB -->|uses| Embeddings
        Library -->|uses| Embeddings
    end

    Client[Client / Platform Component] -->|POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>POST /v1/guardrail/checks| API

    subgraph "Pre-baked NLP Models (in-container)"
        SpaCy["SpaCy en_core_web_lg<br/>Entity Recognition"]
        SentTrans["Sentence Transformers<br/>Semantic Similarity"]
        FastEmbedModel["FastEmbed / ONNX<br/>Lightweight Embeddings"]
        NLTK["NLTK Data<br/>Tokenization"]
    end

    Embeddings --> SpaCy
    Embeddings --> SentTrans
    Embeddings --> FastEmbedModel
    Library --> SpaCy
    Library --> NLTK

    subgraph "External LLM Providers"
        OpenAI["OpenAI API"]
        NIM["NVIDIA NIM"]
        AzureOAI["Azure OpenAI"]
        AnthropicAPI["Anthropic API"]
        CohereAPI["Cohere API"]
        vLLM["vLLM / TRT-LLM"]
    end

    Engine -->|LLM inference<br/>HTTPS/443| OpenAI
    Engine -->|LLM inference| NIM
    Engine -->|LLM inference<br/>HTTPS/443| AzureOAI
    Engine -->|LLM inference<br/>HTTPS/443| AnthropicAPI
    Engine -->|LLM inference<br/>HTTPS/443| CohereAPI
    Engine -->|LLM inference| vLLM

    Redis["Redis<br/>6379/TCP"]
    OTELCollector["OpenTelemetry Collector"]

    API -.->|thread state persistence| Redis
    Tracing -.->|trace export| OTELCollector

    PlatformIngress["RHOAI Platform Ingress<br/>TLS Termination"] -->|HTTP/8000| API

